description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 arranged songs, navigators, and avatars from Touhou Project ~ The Embodiment of Scarlet Devil!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
・Hitorishizuka
・Cirno's Perfect Math Class
・Burnt Black, the End of Frozen Beauty
・Epicurus' Rainbow Can No Longer Be Seen
・7 days a week
・The Maid and the Pocket Watch of Blood
・tete+a+tete
・Mischievous Sensation
・And Then There Were None
・？？？（Secret）

■Navigator
・Sakuya
・Frandre

■Avatar
・CIRNO(2D)
・SAKUYA(3D)
・REMILIA(3D)
・FRANDRE(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: Touhou Project Arrangements Pack 1
